  "content": {
    "visible_text": "{\"id\":4543,\"date\":\"2020-05-06T08:41:24\",\"date_gmt\":\"2020-05-06T15:41:24\",\"guid\":{\"rendered\":\"https:\\/\\/quantumsf.org\\/?page_id=4543\"},\"modified\":\"2023-09-11T14:17:06\",\"modified_gmt\":\"2023-09-11T21:17:06\",\"slug\":\"kids-distance-learning\",\"status\":\"publish\",\"type\":\"page\",\"link\":\"https:\\/\\/quantumsf.org\\/kids-martial-arts\\/kids-distance-learning\\/\",\"title\":{\"rendered\":\"Distance-learning resources\"},\"content\":{\"rendered\":\"<h4>Kids Program Forms, ages 6\\u20139<\\/h4>\\n<p>The following forms lessons were filmed during an online Forms Seminar\\u00a0 on May 16, 2020.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\n<p class=\\\"wp-block-paragraph\\\">These distance-learning resources were developed during the Shelter-in-Place ordinances of the 2020 Covid-19 pandemic. They don&#8217;t function as replacements to our in-person classes, but remain available for our students who would like to do supplemental martial arts at home.<\\/p>\\n<p><\\/p>\\n<p>To view the written steps to each form, short videos of each form as it is to be performed, and the techniques learned at each rank, please click through the <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/quantumsf.org\\/kids-teens-martial-arts-curriculum\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">Kids Curriculum page<\\/a>, choosing the belt your student is *<em>currently<\\/em>* wearing.<\\/p>\\n<p>View a big-picture overview of the <a title=\\\"KIDS_curriculum_poster\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/quantumsf.org\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/06\\/kids_curriculum_poster.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">Kids Program rank belt curriculum here<\\/a>. Consider downloading and printing it for visual motivation!<\\/p>\\n<h5>Basic Form: White Belt<\\/h5>\\n<p><span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/QgbrU1bZ4GA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n\\n<hr class=\\\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\\\"\\/>\\n\\n\\n\\n<h5 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Chon-Ji: Yellow Belt<\\/h5>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/aDTWTdZBQ8I?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<hr class=\\\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\\\"\\/>\\n\\n\\n\\n<h5 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Dan Gun: High Yellow Belt<\\/h5>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/z1BDZEl9-o8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<hr class=\\\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\\\"\\/>\\n\\n\\n\\n<h5 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Do San: Green Belt<\\/h5>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/1hoFY11T6jM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<hr class=\\\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\\\"\\/>\\n\\n\\n\\n<h5 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Gravity: High Green Belt<\\/h5>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/7BjZkGH14Nw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<hr class=\\\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\\\"\\/>\\n\\n\\n\\n<h5 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Terra Moto: Blue Belt<\\/h5>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/MLHid0GBMYc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p class=\\\"wp-block-paragraph\\\"><\\/p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<hr class=\\\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\\\"\\/>\\n\\n\\n\\n<h5 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Kids Classes<\\/h5>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p class=\\\"wp-block-paragraph\\\">Below is a collection of one-hour-long classes that each begin with a 30 minute warmup\\/stretching session, followed by a 30 minute martial arts lesson. These videos are intended to support students with continued practice during times they are not able to make it to the Dojo, such as vacations or quarantine periods.&nbsp;The videos are recordings of live Zoom classes broadcast from the San Francisco Dojo during Spring 2020, when we were closed due to the COVID-19 pandemic. <\\/p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\